title: Metal Bastard's Pacific Northwest Compilations (grunge etc)
description:
Two compilations I made of various pacific northwest region bands from circa 1985-1995, in tribute of two great books: Greg Prato's Grunge Is Dead: The Oral History of Seattle Rock Music and Mark Yarm's Everybody Loves Our Town: An Oral History of Grunge. Read both.

The bands included: 

7 Year Bitch
The Blackouts
Cat Butt
Crackerbash
Dead Mean
Dickless
The Fartz
Fecal Matter
Flop
Girl Trouble
The Gits
Green River
Love Battery
Malfunkshun
The Melvins
Mono Men
Mudhoney
Nirvana
Pearl Jam
Screaming Trees
Seaweed
Skin Yard
Some Velvet Sidewalk
Soundgarden
The Supersuckers
Swallow
TAD
The Thrown Ups
The U-Men
Wipers
Young Fresh Fellows
